      <img src="https://placeholder.v0.dev/1200x800.jpg" alt="Oracle in action">
    </div>

    <div class="about-text">
      <h3>The Science Behind the Oracle</h3>
      <p>Our Oracle combines advanced algorithms with cosmic pattern recognition to provide definitive yes or no answers to your questions. Unlike other decision-making tools that leave you with ambiguity, the Oracle gives you clarity.</p>

      <p>Each answer is accompanied by detailed reasoning that explains the factors considered in reaching the conclusion. This transparency helps you understand not just what the answer is, but why it's the right answer for you.</p>

      <p>Whether you're making personal decisions, business choices, or simply satisfying your curiosity, the Oracle provides the guidance you need with confidence and precision.</p>

      <a href="#features" class="cta-btn">Explore Features</a>
    </div>
  </div>
